{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Hidden Ones is a 3D action fighting game featuring a myth-inspired martial arts aesthetic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/extras/Wishlist.jpg?t=1735642540\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Captivating Outcast stories and fast-paced combat </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unveil the ancient myths of the Outcast world and engage in electrifying combat across diverse game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Myth and martial arts combined in cinematic design </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience unique Eastern martial arts combat, featuring enticing cinematic scenes inspired by an urban myth with ancient elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Completely fair PvP experience </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The core values of The Hidden Ones focus on ensuring fair competitive play and upholding a strict zero-tolerance policy against cheating.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Mode: Story</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Various boss mechanics and designs reflect the different chapters of the mythical martial arts story. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience cinematic-style cutscenes and beautifully-designed levels that immerse players in the action. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Venture into the world of The Outcast through action-packed battles and explore the story from multiple perspectives.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/extras/PVE.gif?t=1735642540\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Mode: Duel </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in high-intensity battles and adapt in the blink of an eye. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By integrating other characters' skills into the action roulette, players can gain a game-changing advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use unique skills and strategies in a fair and competitive environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/extras/PvP.gif?t=1735642540\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Mode: Trial Mode </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Conquer all the epic bosses that emerge throughout the story mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle bosses that grow stronger with each fight, mastering different characters and battle styles to prevail.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/extras/Ultimate.gif?t=1735642540\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735642540","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735642540","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/67bdfe86e87a8a7922c4c9457ebd8c62e7f2eb70/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735642540","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3345210/67bdfe86e87a8a7922c4c9457ebd8c62e7f2eb70/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735642540","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op"